{"tid":1432112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有團體到警總外表達「十一大訴求」 包括重啟《逃犯條例》修訂","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T14:23:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"71050f9f1eabcc882cad9f7fb5744a5da5aeae53","tid":1432112,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:04:43.000Z","msg":"有團體到警察總部外表達「十一大訴求」，過百名市民參與。<span style=\"color: red;\">訴求包括重啟《逃犯條例》修訂、成立獨立調查委員會追查泛民議員有否參與及協助暴亂、制定「禁止示威蒙面法」及辱警罪，以及開發香港電台公眾使用權等等。</span><br />\n<br />\n「香港政研會」稱早前收集9萬名市民意見，綜合意見後得出「十一大訴求」，發言人鄧德成說，警察代表法治，侮辱警察等於侮辱法治。另外，他指香港電台現時是「單聲道」，沒有反映支持政府的聲音，作為公營媒體，應該開放廣播時間給市民大眾反映不同意見。<br />\n<br />\n被問到如何收集到9萬名市民意見，發言人指是在撐警集會中收集。對於要求重啟條例修訂是否與政府「唱反調」，發言人説社會有需要的話，就應該向政府提出訴求。另外，對於獨立調查委員會是否需要調查元朗7.21襲擊事件，發言人表示理解社會上有這訴求，但不在團體的訴求中。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YLnyF4j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYLnyF4j.jpg&h=1e8a217f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473439-20190808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473439-20190808.htm&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7xTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=6e038f85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473439-20190808.htm&h=4fa250a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473439-20190808.htm</a>"},{"pid":"7293eac40329da7d4f4c5caa38c03e5fc76b6560","tid":1432112,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:05:35.000Z","msg":"「十一大民間訴求」<br />\n1.重啟《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n2.確認612為暴動<br />\n3.追究所有612及之後為違法暴徒刑責<br />\n4.成立獨立調查委員會追查泛民議員有否參與及協助暴亂<br />\n5.追討遊行集會申請人有關活動導致公共設施損毀復修費用<br />\n6.要求警隊加強執法 嚴厲打擊一切暴力衝擊違法行為<br />\n7.馬上展開23條立法程序<br />\n8.制定【禁止示威蒙面法】<br />\n9.制定【禁止侮辱執法公職人員法】<br />\n10.徹查外國反華組織資金在港流向<br />\n11.開發【香港電台】公眾使用權<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245e9896ddd14fe8fb29069cf12d4a3ca0a7e344","tid":1432112,"uid":249794,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"班狗心諗 咪撚搞鳩我啦 又要再做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862f067561bea30003138552f5d1134da1727a28","tid":1432112,"uid":229289,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"又準備彈匣"},{"pid":"b8cd52ab524bc77591d8fb8b1b7dfddd7808dad9","tid":1432112,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"1.重啟《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n7.馬上展開23條立法程序<br />\n<br />\n打孖上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死"},{"pid":"fe6fdc7cf7020e45e03414b6412d42ef708c11a6","tid":1432112,"uid":214192,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b8cd52ab524bc77591d8fb8b1b7dfddd7808dad9","tid":1432112,"uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:07:42.000Z","msg":"1.重啟《逃犯條例》修訂<br />\n7.馬上展開23條立法程序<br />\n<br />\n打孖上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:09:27.000Z","msg":"政府仲唔快啲重啓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下一重啓會有咩事發生"},{"pid":"2674554f4c9abce130a24c7b4f714542bc28541f","tid":1432112,"uid":87068,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:10:59.000Z","msg":"佢地去警察總部做咩？<br />\n話俾大家聽香港依家係軍警治港囉！<br />\n<br />\n警察做埋林奠嗰分<br />\n名正言順做香港最高權力核心"},{"pid":"09322f3c687501a53c887c107e5b426aed5c274f","tid":1432112,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201